<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hartmut Fuchs von Dornheim zu Neidenfels</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, nach seiner Rückkehr den Hans Fridecker, Bürger zu Nürnberg, zu befragen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_242" id="120v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_242_r1l1"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hartmüt fuchs von Dornheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r1l2">cʒü Neydenfels geſeʒʒen / . </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_242_r1l3"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> her Hartmüt / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von <expan>Hanſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Frıdeck<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r1l4"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> / . Derſelb vnſer <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> ıſt cʒü der cʒeıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r1l5">nicht anheim / . Aber wenn er herheim kümt / ſo <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r1l6">Jn <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief hören laſſen / vnd ew <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> ein antwurt laſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r1l7"><expan>wiſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> / ob vns dann <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> daran manet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_242_r1l8">vnd ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>t</expan> / . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vj̃ . <expan>An<ex>te</ex></expan> Judıca </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_242" id="120v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hartmüt Fuchs von Dornheim, czü Neydenfels
                        gesezzen</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> her Hartmüt, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von
                                <expan>Hanse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Frideck<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>; derselb
                        unser <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> ist czü der czeit nicht anheim. Aber
                        wenn er herheim kümt, so <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir in
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief hören lassen und ew
                                <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> ein antwurt lassen
                                <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan>, ob uns dann
                            <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> daran manet und ein
                            <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>vord<ex>er</ex>t</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> judica.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
